Description: IES-3240 is an managed Redundant Ring Ethernet switch with 24x10/100Base-T(X) ports. All function of IES-3240 can be managed centralized and convenient by a powerful windows utility — Open-Vision. In addition, the wide operating temperature range from -40 to 70°C can satisfy most of operating environment. Therefore, the switch is one of the most reliable choice for highly-managed Ethernet application.
